{
  "texts": [
    "These 66 articles were then subjected to further examination of their titles, abstracts, and full-texts, as illustrated in Figure 1.",
    "For example, some review articles (e.g., Jan et al. 2023) although mentioned keywords such as AI and CC were not focused on the construction industry.",
    "Other articles that did not focus on AI and CC in the CI were deleted.",
    "For instance, Lian's (2022) study was related to AI and CC in a construc-tion-related context but mainly focused on blockchain platforms and associated technologies.",
    "Some of these articles were excluded in this study."
  ]
}